               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I am very sorry, but coming from my work at the time, I saw a boy of the name of Clarke who asked me to pawn them—I did so, but did not know he had stolen them—I have good friends, but they are not here—I live with my mother.</p>
